Amusing myself with snow.

Wikipedia page on linkages: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linkage_(mechanical)
For more in-depth information about the mathematics of linkages, go to 16:05 in this lecture: http://courses.csail.mit.edu/6.849/fall10/lectures/L08.html
